text: Indian J Microbiol https://doi.org/10.1007/s12088-021-00950-6 Correction to: The snogI Gene is Necessary for the Proper Functioning of the Nogalamycin Biosynthesis Pathway Accepted: 28 May 2021 (cid:2) Association of Microbiologists of India 2021 Correction to: Indian J Microbiol The original version of this article was published on 7th May, 2021, unfortunately contained several errors.
